                <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="file:/C:/Users/Filip/Desktop/cwiczenie/ewa-boloz/Topics/Ho%20to%20create%20a%20perfect%20screenshot/t_how%20to_4_editing.dita" xtrc="li:5;46:21">Try to do not scale the image too much afterward. But if you must, avoid the
                    dreaded pixelation. Try resizing your picture or screenshot in an image editing
